2|14|Waitha laqoo allatheena amanoo qaloo amanna waitha khalaw ila shayateenihim qaloo inna maAAakum innama nahnu mustahzioona
2|15|Allahu yastahzio bihim wayamudduhum fee tughyanihim yaAAmahoona
